Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:39.01,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}柔和的微风吹拂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:41.83,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}开辟崭新的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:44.67,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无论何时那条道路
