Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚喝了水果蜜瓜酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的事 就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸吧 {\fs70}现充！{\fs50}现充！！{\fs30}现充！！！{\fs10}现充！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么觉得只是旁观就变得很不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日高同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你对秋穗也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…喵在说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是该期待「其实你是对八汐学长暗藏情思」的发展？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说喜欢八汐学长的是古郡你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 既然这样 围成一个圈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借着梦想与友情的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央种子岛机器人部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元气一发！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐心合力！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说这是拯救世界的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说全人类的希望都寄托在了你们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:16.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all right all right 再过一点 好停！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒数！Three Two One！Lift Off！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对于我来说 这些事情索然无味…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光枪座
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经朝向Thunder Emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…装载完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,System Link Online
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有线连接口袋电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连红色的线哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围地图 载入开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.36,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光扫描器左右均无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3M 5 7 10 15 20 范围最大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地形判断用AI 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海 一上来就要动真格 能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事一开始就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要事到如今才跟我说No Go啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Condition All Green 最终判断 Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNVARREL！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动！

